{"tid":692952,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"［冇圖］白滑 粉嫩 多汁 大波  相見在阿活","createTime":"2018-06-07T05:29:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-08T06:23:01.000Z","uid":5422,"like":19,"dislike":59,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"1ab8ef9386262643b165d255c4eea179404c47ed","tid":692952,"uid":5422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T05:29:11.000Z","msg":"是咁的 事源小弟多年冇食 美心 嗰啲港式快餐店好幾年 <br />\n所以依家就特登去尋找翻當年嘅味道 <br />\n琴日食咗大家樂個南洋咖哩飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 搞到我肚痛 <br />\n今日就冒死去大快活 食返個雞胸紅米飯 究竟係咪真係咁好食？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/07/130105_44faf888ad32cc188a90d7d09b833b56.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F07%2F130105_44faf888ad32cc188a90d7d09b833b56.png&h=f52370ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n嗌左坐低先發現 原本嘅南瓜汁 轉左做山楂汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/07/130540_8a1b6d97144f6226e50a14ca75bb65e0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F07%2F130540_8a1b6d97144f6226e50a14ca75bb65e0.png&h=99d25e52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n個賣相有少少差 但一食啖雞胸肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/07/130922_ee625d939f9b67a6d3b315e3efe2cddf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F07%2F130922_ee625d939f9b67a6d3b315e3efe2cddf.png&h=d16c2f3a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n嚿雞胸肉勁滑又多汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 配酸酸甜甜嘅山渣汁一齊食 直頭係絕頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n紅米飯又粒粒分明 唔會太乾或者太濕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大快活真係好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n大家樂就真係狗也不屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/07/131615_22947c81282353365f5f385ce7c546f3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F07%2F131615_22947c81282353365f5f385ce7c546f3.png&h=2eff8690&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n同場加推菠蘿咕嚕肉 一樣咁正<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcd39979f33736fd08998466e3202fe33194b195","tid":692952,"uid":135336,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T05:31:03.000Z","msg":"請問大波係for啲乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bab042baf1e1cec4cd1a4d0a791b7c8cf88ce73","tid":692952,"uid":21423,"like":3,"dislike":11,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T05:31:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"27ee60df17f684644e329369d6918f28d3fae1fc","tid":692952,"uid":5422,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"fcd39979f33736fd08998466e3202fe33194b195","tid":692952,"uid":135336,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T05:31:03.000Z","msg":"請問大波係for啲乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T05:32:22.000Z","msg":"嚿雞胸仲唔夠大嚿咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e716dcae2c84c96561a22e39cdcbc0298587e1e","tid":692952,"uid":40317,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy